                            <comment id="13500053" author="celestin" created="Mon, 19 Nov 2012 06:47:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem seems to come from the parent &lt;tt&gt;pom&lt;/tt&gt;, where two properties are defined&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;properties&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    ...
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;commons.encoding&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;iso-8859-1&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/commons.encoding&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;commons.docEncoding&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;${commons.encoding}&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/commons.docEncoding&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    ...
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;which are then used&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;build&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    ...
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;pluginManagement&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;plugins&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        ...
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;plugin&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;maven-javadoc-plugin&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;version&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;${commons.javadoc.version}&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!-- keep only errors and warnings --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;quiet&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;true&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/quiet&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;encoding&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;${commons.encoding}&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/encoding&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;docEncoding&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;${commons.docEncoding}&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/docEncoding&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            ...
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Therefore, to fix this bug, it should be sufficient to override &lt;tt&gt;commons.encoding&lt;/tt&gt; in our &lt;tt&gt;pom&lt;/tt&gt;, and remove the following lines&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;properties&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    ...
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;project.build.sourceEncoding&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;UTF-8&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/project.build.sourceEncoding&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;project.reporting.outputEncoding&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;UTF-8&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/project.reporting.outputEncoding&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    ...
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/properties&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
